T*
(miner. It does not introduce a separate block format or alternate validation pipeline. If a GPU) Tj
T*
(backend is unavailable or fails policy checks, runtime behavior is controlled by explicit) Tj
T*
(fallback and strictness flags.) Tj
T*
() Tj
