T*
() Tj
T*
(Treat GPU mining as a controlled acceleration feature:) Tj
T*
(- keep reproducible build artifacts,) Tj
T*
(- keep pin metadata synchronized,) Tj
T*
(- enforce preflight probe + strict audit in deployment pipelines,) Tj
T*
(- maintain documented fallback behavior so operators know exactly what happens under backend) Tj
T*
(failure.) Tj
T*
() Tj
